Package: anMC
Type: Package
Title: Compute high dimensional orthant probabilities
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dario Azzimonti
Date: 30-04-2017
Maintainer: Dario Azzimonti <dario.azzimonti@gmail.com>
Description: Computationally efficient method to estimate orthant probabilities
    of high-dimensional Gaussian vectors. This method is used in the function conservativeEstimates to compute conservative estimates of excursion sets under Gaussian random field priors. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    mvtnorm
Imports:
    microbenchmark,
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.1)
Suggests:
    DiceKriging
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
